text: I finally got my first real  proper job TL DR  My first job has reignited my love for life   Not expecting many people to care about this but I finally got a job  I left school almost a year ago now and it s been super difficult finding a job because of my age  location and this little thing that happened that you might ve missed  think it s a global pandemic or something  idk   But now I work in a garden centre and honestly it s very chill and I high key love it  It s very tiring though  like I thought I was tired after school but oh boy that was nothing compared to this  Not every job will be like that and I do still enjoy what I do  even if I ve only been there for one day Sooooo yeah  if u read then thanks for reading  Just wanted to share my joy I guess  Just remember there is a world beyond school  and life is friggin awesome in it
summary: I left school almost a year ago and it was difficult to find a job. Now I work in a garden centre and I love it. Not every job will be like that and I do still enjoy what I do even if I've only been there for one day.
